        <div class="faq-toggle">+</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Fixed patrols occur at scheduled times following a set route, providing visible security at predictable intervals. Random patrols happen at varying times with different routes, creating unpredictability that better deters potential criminal activity. We can implement either strategy based on your specific security needs.</p>
