        <p>Our patrol officers document each visit with digital time stamps, photographs, and detailed notes. You'll receive a comprehensive report after each patrol that includes arrival/departure times, observations, any incidents or concerns, actions taken, and recommendations. Reports are delivered electronically through our secure client portal.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
